{"word":"G3342 - μεταξύ - metaxý - met-ax-oo' - Between","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεταξύ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">metaxý</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">met-ax-oo'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Between</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"இல், நடுவே, அடுத்த - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"between"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3326 - μετά - metá - met-ah'/3326\">G3326</a> and a form of <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a>; <i>betwixt</i> (of place or person); (of time) as adjective <i>intervening</i>, or (by implication) <i>adjoining:</i> - between, mean while, next.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}